text:
Hey, I'm Kasey, the founder of Atro. I'm on a mission to make security easier for smaller businesses.

I've been in security a while now an realized that the major barriers to for smaller teams to get secure are cost and complexity. So I set out to break these barriers down. We've built a platform that helps teams understand and fix the security issues they have in an easy self-guided way. Our beta is out and I'm looking for feedback. Check it out!
